      {
        "type": "rule",
        "text": "At the start of the battle, you can set up one Teleport Homer token for this unit anywhere on the battlefield that is not in your opponent\u2019s deployment zone. If you do, once per battle, you can target this unit with the Rapid Ingress Stratagem for 0CP, but when resolving that Stratagem, you must set this unit up within 3\" of that token and not within 9\" of any enemy models. That token is then removed.",
        "name": "Teleport Homer"
      },
      {
        "type": "rule",
        "text": "Each time a model in this unit makes an attack that targets your Oath of Moment target , add 1 to the Hit roll .",
